{"tid":2336862,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"早備餐單等12人回港","createTime":"2020-12-23T02:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T03:16:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2d5db836f86fbbbb8d2902207a4db96171abd70d","tid":2336862,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T02:05:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201223/5XPLLT6RHVGMTNNQ7VPG3RGE4Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201223%2F5XPLLT6RHVGMTNNQ7VPG3RGE4Q%2F&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=e1b87fc0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201223%2F5XPLLT6RHVGMTNNQ7VPG3RGE4Q%2F&h=2d15ee20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201223/5XPLLT6RHVGMTNNQ7VPG3RGE4Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n早備餐單等12人回港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NaaPS9LbteZ2w3dj8E3bglh3nZs=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QJXG7ASHR5HEZBZCXAA7EMQWKU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNaaPS9LbteZ2w3dj8E3bglh3nZs%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQJXG7ASHR5HEZBZCXAA7EMQWKU.jpg&h=fbd0bb0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■阿一（右）計劃明年推出App作跨區服務，銀丁（左）則為12名港人預備了一個「12人到會」。<br />\n<br />\n今年8月，12名港人被指潛逃台灣途中遭內地公安拘捕，至今一直被秘密關押逾100日。今個聖誕，12名港人仍身陷囹圄之中，不知歸期何年何月何日。「將軍澳外賣專線」成員阿一說，專線不只是一個外賣平台，「而係都一直帶緊好強訊息畀人，有啲嘢係唔可以忘記」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：五食肆首創聯合到會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n白色恐怖瀰漫 堅守原則<br />\n<br />\n專線一個最大心願是為12名港人預備了一個「12人到會」，「一直都預備好，但（12名港人）仲未落到嚟食，呢個set（餐）好想佢哋嚟食到，係我哋最大心願」。至於到會餐單內容，他稱要保持神秘，「希望有一日佢哋可以食到」。<br />\n<br />\n阿一認為，自港區國安法在港實施以來，社會充斥白色恐怖。「有啲擔心會被打壓，所以有請教專業人士點樣冇咁大風險，公。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n但他承認，政權若有一天要全面打壓，「我哋做乜都冇用，點做足。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"081fb3f71c9188e40227cd95a71a218ab5e9a28b","tid":2336862,"uid":52705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T03:16:57.000Z","msg":"將軍澳<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}